# Simulate shared-secret flags

For local `simulate` runs, prefer skipping the interactive phrase prompt:

- `./conversation-stenography simulate -dev-secret` — built-in phrase `local-dev-only-not-for-real-chat`
- `./conversation-stenography simulate -secret '…'` — explicit phrase
- `./conversation-stenography simulate -manual` — show covers only; decode with `/paste` as the other person

Do not use `-dev-secret` for real chat / production. Do not combine `-dev-secret` with `-secret`.
